t we already have four pawns for the piece.}) 16... Qa3 $15 {[%csl Re2][%cal Ra3a6,Gf8c5] Both kings are pretty shaky here, but we have the stronger threats at the moment, and also an objective advantage, which probably doesn't mean anything at all, since it is very easy to go wrong with both colours.} *

