then the IQP can go forward.} 12. Qa4 d4 $1 {[%csl Rc3] There is no need to wait, we can achieve a great position after this move.} 13. Ne4 Nxe4 14. Bxe4 Re8 {[%cal Re8e4] We are improving our position with every move, which can't be said about White, since we are keeping busy our opponent with one move threats.} 15. Bg2 Qf6 $15 {[%cal Ge8e2,Ga8e8,Yg4f3] Black is comfortably better, we can play ...[Re2] next and then double on the e-file, ...[Bf3] is also an idea to make the light squares weaker.} *

