good at all.} Ng4 $1 {[%cal Rg4f2,Rc5f2,Gf7f5,Ge5e4] Because of this immediate attack, White has concrete problems to solve.} 11. Ne4 {[%csl Gf2][%cal Re4c5,Ge4f2] Even though White gains a tempo on the bishop, the knight is on the way of ...[f5]-[e4].} (11. O-O $2 f5 $1 {-+ With ...[e4] coming next, Black has a huge and winning attack.}) 11... Bd4 {[%cal Gf7f5,Rf5e4]} 12. h3 Nh6 $17 {[%cal Gf7f5,Ge5e4] Leaving the way free for the f-pawn. White is in trouble, because ...[f5]-[e4] is coming with great power.} *

