. White will have a tough time to defend the king.}) 13... Nxe4 $1 {[%csl Ye1][%cal Gd8h4,Gf8e8] Very nice! Everything is hanging, but nothing can be taken. 🙂} 14. Be3 (14. fxg4 Qh4+ {+ -+ Black will pick up the rook on [h1].}) 14... Re8 $36 {[%csl Re1,Ye2,Ye3][%cal Gd8h4,Gd6c5] With such a weak king, it doesn't look good for our opponent.} *

