[%csl Gh2][%cal Yh2f3,Yd7h3,Rh2f1] The knight is unusual but very dangerous on [h2], with ideas like ...[Bxh3] or ...[Nf3]+ at some moment.} 14. Re1 Qh4 $17 {[%csl Gd6,Gd7,Gh4,Gh2][%cal Gf7f5,Gf5f4,Gf4f3] Next is to push the f-pawn till [f3]. 🙂} (14... Qh4 15. Qxe4 {Loses to} Rae8 16. Qxh4 Rxe1#) *

