if Black is greedy.} Bxb2 (11... Bb6 $1 12. Nc3 Bd4) 12. f4 {Threatening [e5]. A very serious issue for Black.} d6 (12... Bxa1 13. Qxa1 d6 14. Ng3 {+- With [Nh5] coming next, the computer is already saying that Black is lost!}) 13. Rb1 Rb8 14. Rxb2 {The bishop was an important kingside defender!} Rxb2 15. Ng3 $16 {[%cal Re4e5,Rg3h5] Black's position is super risky, and also objectively bad.} *

