queen did, we have a threat on [f2] right now.} 14. f4 (14. g3 {Weakening the light squares around the king.} Qh3 15. Nd3 c5 {∞ If the bishop comes to the long diagonal, it won't be much fun for White.}) 14... Ba6 $1 {[%csl Re1][%cal Rh4e1] Thanks to the loose rook on [e1]!} 15. Qf2 Qxf2+ 16. Kxf2 Nd5 {[%cal Rd5f4,Rf8f4]} 17. g3 Rae8 18. Kg1 g5 $19 {And White can't keep their position together.} *

