, but there is no need to sacrifice a piece here. Of course, the lines can still be pretty fun.} 15. bxa5 Ba6 {∓}) 15. O-O Nd5 {[%csl Gc4,Gd5][%cal Gf8e8,Gc8f5] Just by occupying the weak squares, Black has tremendous compensation for the pawn.} *

