 O-O {could be met by} g6 $1 {winning a piece.}) 17... Nd8 18. O-O Nf7 $132 {[%csl Rh4][%cal Yg7g6,Yg6g5] With a complex position; Black has both ...[g5] and ...[g6] as an idea in the next move.} *

