 Black should go for a slightly worse endgame with} Bxc2 {.}) 11. Bb3 ({•} 11. exd6 Qxd6 $1 12. Bb3 Nce5 $1 {⩱ White has serious problems on [f3].}) ({•} 11. Nxe7 Qxe7 12. exd6 cxd6 13. Bb3 Nce5 {⩱ Again, [f3] is under serious pressure.}) 11... Ncxe5 {[%cal Re5f3,Rg6h4]} 12. h3 {Sacrificing a pawn for a strong centre.} Nxf3+ 13. gxf3 Bxh3 14. f4 h5 $132 {[%csl Ge4,Gf4][%cal Yh3g4] Neither side can be too unhappy with this extremely wild position.} *

