ing material.} 23. g3 Ng2 24. Nxf3 Nxe1 25. Qxe1 Rxf3 {-+ or 24.Re7 Bc6 25.Qb1 Nf4! 26.Qxg6 Nh3}) 21... Qf7 $1 {[%cal Rf7a7,Gh4f3]} (21... Bg2 {was also good.} 22. Rxe8 Bxf1 23. Rxf8+ Kxf8 24. Rxf1 Qc2 {-+}) 22. Rxe8 Nf3+ $1 (22... Nf3+ {White is getting checkmated or losing their queen:} 23. Nxf3 Qxf3 24. Rxf8+ Kxf8 {-+}) 0-1

