shop is also pretty bad.}) 24. Kd3 Rh7 25. Rce1 Kf8 26. Kc4 Rb7 27. Rh3 $2 (27. Bc3 {was the only way to try to defend here.}) 27... Rab8 28. Reh1 e4 $1 {[%cal Rb7b4] ...[Rb4] is checkmate!} 0-1

